This is an avi capture from VHS of the aussie comedy buddies. Quite a good australian comedy/drama movie from the 80's. Anyone who likes The Matrix Trilogy will recognise &quot;The Trainman&quot; as &quot;Ted&quot;, the always-drunk, never-helping guy lol.

Hope you enjoy. If anyone finds a DVD copy please post in comments. I cannot find it at any of my normal stores Ezydvd or Dstore.

